  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chris Conant",
      "poster_handle": "conant_chris"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 07:05:18",
    "text": "Hey Remington, just to confirm - you’re trying to add a screenshot for each template within a theme to display when someone is selecting a template to create a page from?"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 08:32:17",
    "text": "It would be nice to have a “slideshow” feature for the preview. include multiple images in a list in the json file."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chris Conant",
      "poster_handle": "conant_chris"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:45:21",
    "text": "Interesting. Are you thinking of a slideshow of images for a single template?"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chris Conant",
      "poster_handle": "conant_chris"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:45:48",
    "text": "…or are you referring to the theme screenshot and not the templates within a theme?"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:46:01",
    "text": "Theme screen shot"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chris Conant",
      "poster_handle": "conant_chris"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:46:45",
    "text": "Thanks for clarifying. Have you and Remington been talking? He asked for something similar when we were chatting recently, but in regards to the Marketplace."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:47:37",
    "text": "sometimes the theme has many templates, and it would be could to be able to show a few of the templates. I understand you are taking screen shots tho and that could get expensive. I was thinking about letting peeps use images ala wordpress template screenshot file."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:48:10",
    "text": "no. but that is a great example where is would be usefull."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:48:50",
    "text": "I would say to keep processing time down for you guys just let us upload the image and link it via the json file. Just a thought"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chris Conant",
      "poster_handle": "conant_chris"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:49:03",
    "text": "I think that makes sense. I’m passing along the suggestion to the team."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:49:31",
    "edited": {
      "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:49:38"
    },
    "text": "sweet dude. Hope things are going well for you and yours!"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chris Conant",
      "poster_handle": "conant_chris"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:52:18",
    "text": "Thanks Chad! It’s been a while, hope you’re doing well!"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:52:59",
    "text": "Yeah man. Im currently stuck in Colombia, SA"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:53:07",
