  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:53:32",
    "text": "We were on Vacay when this all went down and they locked down the country, NOW untill may 27th :pray:"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:53:47",
    "text": "so I might be able to leave after the first of June."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:54:04",
    "text": "Gonna be a story i tell fo a long time.."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chris Conant",
      "poster_handle": "conant_chris"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:54:20",
    "text": "Oh my goodness, that’s crazy. I’m glad you’re doing well, but that is absolutely wild."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chris Conant",
      "poster_handle": "conant_chris"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:54:26",
    "text": "<@U25C65C3S> you can use `screenshotPath` in a template’s yaml to include a screenshot. For example:\n```&lt;!--\n  templateType: page\n  label: My sweet template\n  screenshotPath: ../images/template-previews/my_image.png\n--&gt;```"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:54:45",
    "text": "yeah man."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:55:09",
    "text": "AND to add top that the syntax im proposing would be :"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:55:17",
    "edited": {
      "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:55:24"
    },
    "text": "```&lt;!--\n  templateType: page\n  label: My sweet template\n  screenshotPath: [../images/template-previews/my_image.png,../images/template-previews/my_image.png,../images/template-previews/my_image.png]\n--&gt;```"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chris Conant",
      "poster_handle": "conant_chris"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2020-05-06 11:55:51",
